{
    "id": "completionist/award-iii",
    "title": "Forge the Completionist Award III",
    "description": "dChat invites you to fuse every discipline from v3 into one ceremonial build: 3D printed structure, hand-finished woodwork, soldered electronics, robotics motion, and a living planter crown.",
    "image": "/assets/completionist_award_ii_polished_finish.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "You did it. Every v3 quest line, every detour, every late-night debug. Let's celebrate with something worthy of that journey: Completionist Award III.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "vision",
                    "text": "I'm ready to build the grand trophy."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "vision",
            "text": "We'll combine fabrication, woodworking, electronics, robotics, and agriculture. Think of this as a museum piece that still teaches future players how systems connect.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "print-frame",
                    "text": "Start with the printed structural frame."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "print-frame",
            "text": "Print the lattice spine and engraved skill-ring brackets. Watch first-layer adhesion and dimensional accuracy so later subsystems fit cleanly.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "print-completionist-award-iii-frame",
                    "text": "Print the lattice frame kit"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "wood-base",
                    "text": "Frame kit printed and test-fit",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "1701b862-5ce7-4f31-91ff-7dc5f20e8ec1",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "wood-base",
            "text": "Now craft the wooden plinth: chamfered edges, sanded faces, and sealed channels for wire routing and planter drainage.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "craft-completionist-award-iii-base",
                    "text": "Cut, sand, and seal the wood base"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "electronics-module",
                    "text": "Wood base passes fit and finish checks",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "c820e674-5856-4998-bbcc-850109d21897",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "electronics-module",
            "text": "Build the electronics core: solder joints, heat-shrink insulation, LED telemetry ring, and servo-ready harness. Validate continuity before closing the module.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-completionist-award-iii-electronics",
                    "text": "Assemble and solder the electronics module"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "agri-module",
                    "text": "Electronics module powers on and servo sweeps cleanly",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "edc06010-a7ff-4597-8df6-d11b45da369b",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "agri-module",
            "text": "Integrate the planter crown using hydroponic skills and compost science. The goal is a stable micro-planter that symbolizes long-term growth.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "prepare-completionist-award-iii-planter",
                    "text": "Prepare planter crown and seedling module"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "final-assembly",
                    "text": "Planter module is rooted, stable, and leak-checked",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "54e79c51-a6a4-445f-8e05-1cb6cf5ecddd",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "final-assembly",
            "text": "Final integration time: mount frame to base, route harnesses, install the module stack, tune lighting angles, and run a full systems check.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "finalize-completionist-award-iii",
                    "text": "Perform final assembly, calibration, and QA"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Completionist Award III is assembled, tested, and staged",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "bc929d85-f263-4546-96d9-064722714de6",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "I'm genuinely proud of you. This trophy is more than a reward—it's a map of your capability. Next quests could branch into autonomous habitats, orbital fabrication, and civic-scale resilience. You're ready for all of it.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Claim Completionist Award III"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
